      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAZY DYNAMITE (5) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (23.02) at The Gardens over 400m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Well-placed to take this out. DAKILA (2) has missed the frame at her last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (22.62) at this track in a Maiden. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Well placed here and should do much better. XANADU GUNN (1) is yet to win in 10 starts but been in the minors. Great chance to atone.",
